This is the stable version with long-term support (LTS). We provide free
maintenance bug fixes until June 2026 and security updates until December 2027.
* Frontend rendering presets
* Content blocks
* Improved search, redirects and workspaces
* Simplified external system integration
* Top-modern image rendering

System requirements
* PHP 8.2, 8.3, 8.4, 8.5
* MariaDB 10.4.3+ / MySQL 8.0.17+ / PostgreSQL 10.0+ / SQLite 3.8.3+
* Modern Browsers
* Detailed list of requirements:
  https://get.typo3.org/version/13#system-requirements
